data.description: Welcome to the perfect investment opportunity you've been waiting for! CASH FLOW! This 2-family home is completely renovated from Head-to-Toe with 3 bedrooms and 1 full bath in each unit. It boasts an inviting open-concept design, complemented by hardwood floors, shaker, soft-close cabinetry, stainless appliances, and hook-up in each unit for laundry. Newer Flat Roof all sealed, cleaned, fully maintenanced. Notably, the basement has been waterproofed & features two sump pumps, ensuring a dry & secure environment. Enhanced with some recent window replacements in 2023, this property not only promises reliable cash flow but also long-term durability & energy efficiency. Situated in a location with access to amenities & transportation, this multifamily gem in Roselle stands as an enticing opportunity for investors to capitalize on the thriving rental market while enjoying the comfort & security of a well-maintained property.
